OL,3,CThe five scams of Christmas and how to
OL,4,Cavoid them
OL,6,FFraud is an ever-present danger in the
OL,7,Fmodern world but in the run-up to
OL,8,FChristmas, scammers come out in droves
OL,9,Fto exploit the gift-giving frenzy and
OL,10,Femotions that come with the festive
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FThe Financial Conduct Authority (FCA)
OL,14,Fwarned earlier this month scammers
OL,15,Fwill be looking to exploit the
OL,16,Ffinancial stress of Christmas.
OL,18,FNationwide, Lloyds, Experian and HSBC
OL,19,Fhave all put out warnings over the
OL,20,Fthreat of scams in recent weeks.
